---
title: AIDA C4 Level 1 Context Diagram
---
graph TB
    classDef user fill:#1e2e3a,stroke:#60a5fa,stroke-width:3px,color:#fff
    classDef system fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#f472b6,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    classDef external fill:#2e1e1e,stroke:#f87171,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    DE["Data Engineer<br/>Explore lineage<br/>Understand impact<br/>NL queries via MIMIR"]
    DA["Data Analyst<br/>Trace data origins<br/>Validate changes"]
    DBA["DBA / Architect<br/>System-wide data flow<br/>Refactoring planning"]
    OPS["Ops / DevOps<br/>Health monitoring<br/>Admin operations"]

    AIDA["AIDA Platform<br/>Lineage Intelligence<br/>for Legacy SQL<br/>SEER Studio first product"]

    SRCDB[("Source Databases<br/>Oracle · PostgreSQL<br/>ClickHouse<br/>JDBC fetch")]
    CLAUDE["Anthropic Claude API<br/>LLM tier 1<br/>Tool calling"]
    OLLAMA["Ollama local<br/>LLM tier 2<br/>Qwen fallback"]
    KC["Keycloak 26.2<br/>Auth provider<br/>realm seer"]
    GH["GitHub<br/>GHCR · Actions<br/>CI/CD"]

    DE -->|HTTPS| AIDA
    DA -->|HTTPS| AIDA
    DBA -->|HTTPS| AIDA
    OPS -->|HTTPS admin| AIDA

    AIDA -->|JDBC fetch SQL| SRCDB
    AIDA -->|HTTPS tool calls| CLAUDE
    AIDA -->|HTTP fallback| OLLAMA
    AIDA -->|JWT JWKS| KC
    AIDA -.->|Docker images| GH

    class DE,DA,DBA,OPS user
    class AIDA system
    class SRCDB,CLAUDE,OLLAMA,KC,GH external
